  "time_ut": 1661246432,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0dbd\u0dd2 \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0da7\u0dda \u0d91\u0db1\u0da2\u0dba\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dbb\u0dba\u0dda \u0dc3\u0ddc\u0dbb\u0d9a\u0db8\u0da7 \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dca \u0d86\u0dbb\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0d9a 02\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d87\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dc5\u0dd4 03\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d85\u0dad\u0dca\u0d85\u0da9\u0d82\u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "03 people, including 02 civil guards, were arrested for theft at Enajaisara in Elephant Fence",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Three people, including two Civil Defense Force soldiers, were arrested yesterday (22nd) on suspicion of theft of an energizer (a device that reduces the electric current and makes it intermittent) which was installed in an electric fence built by the Wildlife Department as a solution to the encroachment of wild elephants. That is said by the Vilachchiya police.",
        "The police say that three persons, including two civil defense soldiers residing at Yaya 6, South Bank, Pemaduwa and a suspect engaged in farming, have been arrested.",
        "The police said that while these two Civil Defense Force soldiers were on duty for the protection of the enajaisera worth 364000 belonging to the wildlife department attached to the electric fence in Degahwa area, Mannaram junction, Wilachchiya police domain, the police said that someone or a group of people broke the front door of the room where it was installed and committed this theft. says",
        "In this regard, after a complaint was made to the Mahavilachchi police by a zoo security officer, the police said that it was revealed that the theft took place when the Civil Defense Force soldiers who were deployed to protect the site left the site for a short time.",
        "The police say that the three suspects were arrested after it was revealed that the Civil Defense Force soldiers had some knowledge of the theft and that the third suspect, the man who lives by farming, is a resident of the area.",
        "The arrested suspects were to be produced in court today (23rd).",
        "A group of Mahavilachchi police officers are conducting further investigations regarding the incident."
      ],
